snippet: The top-ranked Serena Williams appeared to tire against Anabel Medina Garrigues, but she earned two breaks in the third set to reach the Madrid Open semifinals.
abstract: Serena Williams defeats Anabel Medina Garrigues to reach women's semifinals at Madrid Open; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: The top-ranked Serena Williams appeared to tire against Anabel Medina Garrigues, but she earned two breaks in the third set to reach the Madrid Open semifinals.
